                    <em class="parameter"><code>flag</code></em>
                </span></dt><dd><p>Specifies whether the depth buffer is enabled for writing. If
                    <em class="parameter"><code>flag</code></em> is <code class="constant">GL_FALSE</code>,
                    depth buffer writing is disabled, otherwise it is enabled.
                    The initial value is <code class="constant">GL_TRUE</code>.</p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1" title="Description"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
        <code class="function">glDepthMask</code>
        specifies whether the depth buffer is enabled for writing. If
        <em class="parameter"><code>flag</code></em> is <code class="constant">GL_FALSE</code>,
        depth buffer writing is disabled. Otherwise, it is enabled.
        Initially, depth buffer writing is enabled.</p></div><div class="refsect1" title="See Also"><a id="seealso"></a><h2>See Also</h2><p>
